HOW_TO_OPEN_EDITOR

BOILERPLATE

//
// Following are the quicktest variables that are replaced
// as given below:
//
// ___QUICKTEST_PATH___: quicktest directory path
// ___TESTFILEPATH___ : Path to current testfile
// ___TESTPATH___     : Directory where testfiles are present
// ___OUTPUT___       : Output generated by compiling, it's same as ___TESTPATH___/"outfile"
// ___TESTFILENAMEWITHOUTEXTENSION___: Name without extension
// ___TESTFILENAME___ : Name of the testfile without extension
// ___INSTANCE___     : Name of current test instance
// ___FILE_TO_OPEN___ : The file that is going to get opened
//
//
//  e.g.,
//
//   HOW_TO_OPEN_EDITOR    nano ___FILE_TO_OPEN___
//
//  Will open the file with nano text editor
//
